category.category_description: Delicious, freshly made, and oh-so-satisfying. From the Big Mac to our Premium Grilled Chicken Club to our classic Cheeseburger, McDonald’s sandwiches make the meal.
From our ever-popular Chicken McNuggets, our fabulously fresh salads or the classic Filet-O-Fish, both chicken and fish from McDonald’s are delicious choices.

With so many options, mornings have never been tastier. From wholesome choices like Fruit & Maple Oatmeal and the Egg White Delight McMuffin to the savory Sausage Biscuit to the sweet McGriddles sandwich, you'll find exactly what you need to start your morning off just right.
Can a salad be classy? We say yes. Add a little panache to your day with select mixed greens, elegant toppings, and choices galore.
Whether you need a little pick-me-up to get you through the afternoon or a companion for your favorite sandwich, we’ve got you covered.
No meal is complete without a drink! From Diet Coke® to low-fat milk to fresh-brewed hot coffee, we’ve got the perfect companion for your favorite menu items.
Welcome to the world of McCafé. Whether it's our freshly made coffee or our cool Smoothies, rich Shakes or a tasty Frappé, we've got something guaranteed to make your day.
Drop by for a scrumptious pick-me-up.

An empty stomach shouldn’t mean emptying your wallet, too. With the Dollar Menu and More, you can choose from freshly prepared faves like the McChicken or brand new items like the Bacon McDouble. Plus, all your Dollar Menu breakfast favorites are still just a dollar. We’ve never had so many tasty ways to get more for less.
